{"tid":1237944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"同做HA朋友了解過，要睇病人資料其實唔難","createTime":"2019-06-17T16:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T05:15:04.000Z","uid":146803,"like":389,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"24bced672c7845d3c8cd9621d42653e1c503c277","tid":1237944,"uid":146803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:08:17.000Z","msg":"同做HA嘅朋友了解過，小弟試下用最簡單嘅方法解釋下點樣可以睇到病人資料。<br />\n<br />\nLogin window&gt;開software&gt;睇到（完）<br />\n<br />\n部電腦其實擺係急症室嘅公眾地方，醫生護士隨時都要用，所以係長期login唔會logout。今次HA啓動左災難應變，個system就會多左個For police嘅item出黎。<br />\n<br />\n記者會成日話無主動print, 無黑警要求過攞list。<br />\n其實由頭到尾都唔需要print出黎，黑警行過去禁幾個制就可以睇到。<br />\n<br />\n至於點解識禁，有人教or睇過醫護人員禁其實唔難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3711d5400883f84113afccb32bac503482783105","tid":1237944,"uid":118888,"like":134,"dislike":2,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"強烈要求<br />\n查番CCTV睇下邊隻犬<br />\n禁電腦睇"},{"pid":"33ba452b35bf97e9dfbc49374a27c3267bd7d8c0","tid":1237944,"uid":146803,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:11:08.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢沉<br />\n等多d人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f663326f39b4314aa754c6e3358a9c7275f45b5a","tid":1237944,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c52837d98d2d4eb250fcacc06d1095ff863b504f","tid":1237944,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7ed1136ace49c7a2d232306c6ac21594303104","tid":1237944,"uid":215876,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:15:42.000Z","msg":"check cctv"},{"pid":"a9c63c6d1790fd0aa6e826868dfdeb26f6ea25e8","tid":1237944,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:25:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"416cb182409467